{"tid":243044,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"天空是藍色的，係咪歐化中文？","createTime":"2017-05-14T11:19:14.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-16T01:30:14.000Z","uid":30807,"like":12,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4c8df33e8db1b1abd750fcd36b7a142f15076ed6","tid":243044,"uid":30807,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T11:19:14.000Z","msg":"中文應該點講？<br />\n<br />\n仲有咩野係歐化中文<br />\n<br />\n濫用被字？<br />\n<br />\n有冇人解答下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a0d2eeab2d79f95d22d1b758adc04a1e17598b5","tid":243044,"uid":19074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T11:22:15.000Z","msg":"藍色的天空/藍天"},{"pid":"ddf9305f246de49473a8b032cc21f73e14456739","tid":243044,"uid":30807,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T11:32:00.000Z","msg":"歐化中文似乎會多好多<br />\n&quot;被&quot;  &quot;一&quot; &quot;地&quot;<br />\n<br />\n無意義抽象動詞<br />\n<br />\n其實以前D人讀書洗唔洗作文，係咪都限字數?<br />\n<br />\n我覺得依家中小學作文要限字數，有意無意都令人更加習慣歐化中文<br />\n<br />\n本身十隻字寫得完既野，夾硬用十五隻字<br />\n<br />\n利申：唔識，冇研究，純9UP"},{"pid":"6ee5b9e155ddcae43cbd9ca48e23fb96155fdea2","tid":243044,"uid":72301,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T11:48:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>中文應該點講？<br />\n<br />\n仲有咩野係歐化中文<br />\n<br />\n濫用被字？<br />\n<br />\n有冇人解答下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n呢句應該係判斷句 唔算係歐化<br />\n個人覺得最經典嘅歐化例子係「我是一個男孩」<br />\n受英文「I am a boy」個a影響 最正宗應該「我是男孩」就得 <br />\n其他仲有果啲我的「驕傲」啊，不排除xxxx啊果啲<br />\n有興趣可以睇國師啲書 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a52a6ca331b063bb3d40d7a0a4a0b695cea37ac5","tid":243044,"uid":69013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T11:53:10.000Z","msg":"天空是藍色的<br />\n藍色的天空 <br />\n都無問題，唔算歐化中文。"},{"pid":"f63293459b660aac9700f535be92422830de96ca","tid":243044,"uid":3131,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T12:05:32.000Z","msg":"最常見就係既歐化係「被」「一個」「你的、我的」「進行XX」<br />\n係好多時候呢D字都可以唔用 或者本身唔係咁用<br />\n例如:被本身有負面意義 (被殺) <br />\n如果我地有相關意思但係正面既話 可以用「獲」代替<br />\n<br />\n好似上面講既 我是一個男孩 都係常見既歐化<br />\n你緊係一個男孩 唔通你可以係兩個男孩?<br />\n<br />\n你的 我的 好多時候都可以唔用<br />\n例如: 我洗我的手 <br />\n中文好多時候都唔洗講到咁白<br />\n<br />\n進行後面加個動詞亦都係非常核特既中文<br />\n因為進行其實係無意思<br />\n亦都唔需要寫出黎<br />\n例如:進行強姦 同強姦有咩分別?"},{"pid":"4194f7ad3a8249a42465789830b5aaee5117dfe1","tid":243044,"uid":92017,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T12:33:50.000Z","msg":"前排係報紙見到 <span style=\"color: red;\">值得被尊重得職業</span> 其實<span style=\"color: orange;\">值得尊重的職業</span>咪得 個被字好多時都係因為用左英文被動句式黎諗中文<br />\n仲有上面巴打講 忽略左被字既貶義<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">被尊重的xx</span>其幾吊詭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> [sosad <span style=\"color: orange;\">xx備受尊重</span>會好點<br />\n<br />\n仲有好似<span style=\"color: orange;\">被譽為xx</span>又係奇奇怪怪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <span style=\"color: orange;\">有xx之譽</span>咪得<br />\n<br />\n個人覺得<span style=\"color: red;\">他作為神一般的存在</span>呢類acg成日出現既句子都好怪雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <span style=\"color: red;\">他有如神一樣</span>咪得 <span style=\"color: red;\">的存在</span>根本多餘<br />\n<br />\n仲有係國師係中文解毒同執正中文鬧得好多既前返設句，英文會將形容詞放哂係名詞以前，但如果用返同樣方法寫中文會好怪好累贅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好似 <span style=\"color: red;\">這是座長滿樹木，遍佈青草，遊人眾多的出名的山峰</span>累贅到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 又唔出口，完全係佶屈聱牙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n改好少少可以為<span style=\"color: orange;\">這座山十分有名，樹木茂盛，綠草如茵，遊人絡繹不絕</span> 咁樣理應順口好多，國師有講中文用形容詞做後鋪，舒張自然<br />\n<br />\n其他個d一句句子瘋狂用<span style=\"color: red;\">的 地</span>都唔駛點講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n巴打有興趣除左可以睇國師既<span style=\"color: orange;\">中文解毒 執正中文</span>外(除中文同講術數既書外，其他我覺得唔駛理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )，可以一本舊d既 黃維樑教授寫既<span style=\"color: orange;\">清通與多姿</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係一本探討中文寫作 避免歐化同累贅中文既上佳著作<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有興趣睇作家既 可以睇下高手梁實秋既雅舍小品<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n想再進一步研究下，可以睇錢鍾書既作品<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n或者睇下古文觀止都好好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"31fe9c3f78f9eb5599e759aa6d24f4ceeaa59f2b","tid":243044,"uid":92017,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T12:41:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>最常見就係既歐化係「被」「一個」「你的、我的」「進行XX」<br />\n係好多時候呢D字都可以唔用 或者本身唔係咁用<br />\n例如:被本身有負面意義 (被殺) <br />\n如果我地有相關意思但係正面既話 可以用「獲」代替<br />\n<br />\n好似上面講既 我是一個男孩 都係常見既歐化<br />\n你緊係一個男孩 唔通你可以係兩個男孩?<br />\n<br />\n你的 我的 好多時候都可以唔用<br />\n例如: 我洗我的手 <br />\n中文好多時候都唔洗講到咁白<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n進行後面加個動詞亦都係非常核特既中文<br />\n因為進行其實係無意思<br />\n亦都唔需要寫出黎<br />\n例如:進行強姦 同強姦有咩分別?</span></blockquote><br />\n巴打講得好好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而家用名詞代替動詞愈來愈普遍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">進行<span style=\"color: orange;\">創作</span> 進行<span style=\"color: orange;\">教育</span></span> <span style=\"color: orange;\">橙字</span>根本本身就動詞黎既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲有大陸好鍾意既<span style=\"color: red;\">發表講話</span>，<span style=\"color: orange;\">演講</span>唔會好d咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係要跟返make announcement<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n仲有用<span style=\"color: red;\">作為</span>取代<span style=\"color: orange;\">身為</span>，又係跟左英文AS<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n識用標點符號分返開d幾十個字既長句，其實已經好好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f0d0efc4db4b360b8f68ce31b75575494a710cf","tid":243044,"uid":42064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T12:53:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>最常見就係既歐化係「被」「一個」「你的、我的」「進行XX」<br />\n係好多時候呢D字都可以唔用 或者本身唔係咁用<br />\n例如:被本身有負面意義 (被殺) <br />\n如果我地有相關意思但係正面既話 可以用「獲」代替<br />\n<br />\n好似上面講既 我是一個男孩 都係常見既歐化<br />\n你緊係一個男孩 唔通你可以係兩個男孩?<br />\n<br />\n你的 我的 好多時候都可以唔用<br />\n例如: 我洗我的手 <br />\n中文好多時候都唔洗講到咁白<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n進行後面加個動詞亦都係非常核特既中文<br />\n因為進行其實係無意思<br />\n亦都唔需要寫出黎<br />\n例如:進行強姦 同強姦有咩分別?</span></blockquote><br />\n巴打講得好好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n而家用名詞代替動詞愈來愈普遍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">進行<span style=\"color: orange;\">創作</span> 進行<span style=\"color: orange;\">教育</span></span> <span style=\"color: orange;\">橙字</span>根本本身就動詞黎既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲有大陸好鍾意既<span style=\"color: red;\">發表講話</span>，<span style=\"color: orange;\">演講</span>唔會好d咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係要跟返make announcement<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n仲有用<span style=\"color: red;\">作為</span>取代<span style=\"color: orange;\">身為</span>，又係跟左英文AS<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n識用標點符號分返開d幾十個字既長句，其實已經好好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n作為同身為都係as a ....，中文應該避"},{"pid":"aad17e2a9bd03eb448b59dd5ae2f9abafb4f53a9","tid":243044,"uid":42064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T12:57:03.000Z","msg":"「天空是藍色的」 冇問題？可能啦，但怪怪地。<br />\n<br />\n正常會講 「天空很藍」「個天好藍」「個天幾藍」，但d人又可以拗話可能原本冇程度，亂加係曲解"},{"pid":"113eb436cbb32c86a1a60a21ba515b6aca3833b3","tid":243044,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T13:24:44.000Z","msg":"係有啲歐化<br />\n<br />\n'正統'中文我諗應寫'天色蔚藍'"},{"pid":"f68270e1d9a10d67aed8e563f35785d20cb77f2f","tid":243044,"uid":26506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T13:53:34.000Z","msg":"北方化定歐化?"},{"pid":"f981b6474720126fc618dd90ed165aa1d78f5ae6","tid":243044,"uid":19363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T13:57:31.000Z","msg":"藍天"},{"pid":"7a7b6eee8e08e56aa225e0052d0d2feb82592ec2","tid":243044,"uid":26506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T14:02:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係有啲歐化<br />\n<br />\n'正統'中文我諗應寫'天色蔚藍'</blockquote><br />\n&quot;天空是藍色&quot;已經好好多, 北方語/書面語助詞累贅"},{"pid":"a8e4c267672f758c6108ff9fed57e1aa46ccf43f","tid":243044,"uid":73724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T14:18:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>中文應該點講？<br />\n<br />\n仲有咩野係歐化中文<br />\n<br />\n濫用被字？<br />\n<br />\n有冇人解答下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實睇你放句句子嘅重點係邊。中文尤其會將重點要表達嘅野放句子偏後位置。<br />\n例如 天空是藍色的 係主要表達&ldquo;藍色&rdquo;呢個重點；另外呢句野本來已經有主謂賓，好難再加野上去。<br />\n藍色的天空 就純粹用定語去補充主語，後面可以接謂語/賓語等...<br />\n<br />\n換句話說，人地問你個天咩色，唔通你答&ldquo;藍色的天空&rdquo;咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你都係要答天空是藍色的"},{"pid":"19bc36c5322e3c8b3efb9df6c45a515edf639fc2","tid":243044,"uid":8867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T14:18:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"924bbce37d837d954612f8bee3d6699ffd236f72","tid":243044,"uid":73724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T14:26:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>中文應該點講？<br />\n<br />\n仲有咩野係歐化中文<br />\n<br />\n濫用被字？<br />\n<br />\n有冇人解答下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實睇你放句句子嘅重點係邊。中文尤其會將重點要表達嘅野放句子偏後位置。<br />\n例如 天空是藍色的 係主要表達&ldquo;藍色&rdquo;呢個重點；另外呢句野本來已經有主謂賓，好難再加野上去。<br />\n藍色的天空 就純粹用定語去補充主語，後面可以接謂語/賓語等...<br />\n<br />\n換句話說，人地問你個天咩色，唔通你答&ldquo;藍色的天空&rdquo;咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你都係要答天空是藍色的</blockquote><br />\n補充翻，見到有巴打用天空蔚藍或者其他類似嘅句子，我就認為係句式不同。<br />\n天空蔚藍，當中蔚藍係形容天空嘅顏色。如果放喺文章<span style=\"color: red;\">單句</span>使用，係會唔知做咩咁。<br />\n但天空是藍色的，當中藍色係陳述緊天空顏色，佢嘅形容性會因為一個&ldquo;是&rdquo;字降低，所以重點就會放係&ldquo;藍色&rdquo;度，咁藍色會唔會喺係文章中表達出咩意象就另計，但如果獨立成句都絕不過分。"},{"pid":"f32a61c4bbea764767af431026d3cc740437684f","tid":243044,"uid":5431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T14:48:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>前排係報紙見到 <span style=\"color: red;\">值得被尊重得職業</span> 其實<span style=\"color: orange;\">值得尊重的職業</span>咪得 個被字好多時都係因為用左英文被動句式黎諗中文<br />\n仲有上面巴打講 忽略左被字既貶義<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">被尊重的xx</span>其幾吊詭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> [sosad <span style=\"color: orange;\">xx備受尊重</span>會好點<br />\n<br />\n仲有好似<span style=\"color: orange;\">被譽為xx</span>又係奇奇怪怪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <span style=\"color: orange;\">有xx之譽</span>咪得<br />\n<br />\n個人覺得<span style=\"color: red;\">他作為神一般的存在</span>呢類acg成日出現既句子都好怪雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <span style=\"color: red;\">他有如神一樣</span>咪得 <span style=\"color: red;\">的存在</span>根本多餘<br />\n<br />\n仲有係國師係中文解毒同執正中文鬧得好多既前返設句，英文會將形容詞放哂係名詞以前，但如果用返同樣方法寫中文會好怪好累贅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好似 <span style=\"color: red;\">這是座長滿樹木，遍佈青草，遊人眾多的出名的山峰</span>累贅到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 又唔出口，完全係佶屈聱牙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n改好少少可以為<span style=\"color: orange;\">這座山十分有名，樹木茂盛，綠草如茵，遊人絡繹不絕</span> 咁樣理應順口好多，國師有講中文用形容詞做後鋪，舒張自然<br />\n<br />\n其他個d一句句子瘋狂用<span style=\"color: red;\">的 地</span>都唔駛點講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n巴打有興趣除左可以睇國師既<span style=\"color: orange;\">中文解毒 執正中文</span>外(除中文同講術數既書外，其他我覺得唔駛理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )，可以一本舊d既 黃維樑教授寫既<span style=\"color: orange;\">清通與多姿</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係一本探討中文寫作 避免歐化同累贅中文既上佳著作<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有興趣睇作家既 可以睇下高手梁實秋既雅舍小品<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n想再進一步研究下，可以睇錢鍾書既作品<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n或者睇下古文觀止都好好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n余光中本中與西都好好睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18e22d44ba72aeba19591b8a16e8ff0aa6e702f1","tid":243044,"uid":3131,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T15:01:07.000Z","msg":"只要記住中文多用動詞 英文多用名詞<br />\n中文多散句 英文多長句<br />\n無論寫中定英都得心應手"},{"pid":"c01e57b25dd1396ef0cc72ffbb40c3ac387dafd0","tid":243044,"uid":35364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T15:12:06.000Z","msg":"我地讀哲學成日用歐化中文，<br />\n語句越複雜，就越難避免。"},{"pid":"a0557501c596eb9dbb749506a20c8347c3ad5e6a","tid":243044,"uid":35870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T15:12:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8cff7ef62205f1d05e59ffcbd11fe209d6af4b1","tid":243044,"uid":35870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T15:14:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>中文應該點講？<br />\n<br />\n仲有咩野係歐化中文<br />\n<br />\n濫用被字？<br />\n<br />\n有冇人解答下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實睇你放句句子嘅重點係邊。中文尤其會將重點要表達嘅野放句子偏後位置。<br />\n例如 天空是藍色的 係主要表達&ldquo;藍色&rdquo;呢個重點；另外呢句野本來已經有主謂賓，好難再加野上去。<br />\n藍色的天空 就純粹用定語去補充主語，後面可以接謂語/賓語等...<br />\n<br />\n換句話說，人地問你個天咩色，唔通你答&ldquo;藍色的天空&rdquo;咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你都係要答天空是藍色的</blockquote><br />\n補充翻，見到有巴打用天空蔚藍或者其他類似嘅句子，我就認為係句式不同。<br />\n天空蔚藍，當中蔚藍係形容天空嘅顏色。如果放喺文章<span style=\"color: red;\">單句</span>使用，係會唔知做咩咁。<br />\n但天空是藍色的，當中藍色係陳述緊天空顏色，佢嘅形容性會因為一個&ldquo;是&rdquo;字降低，所以重點就會放係&ldquo;藍色&rdquo;度，咁藍色會唔會喺係文章中表達出咩意象就另計，但如果獨立成句都絕不過分。</blockquote><br />\n可唔可以寫成<br />\n天空，青也<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1aefb4c33405ca2e0793f2e4177ffa2812c72b04","tid":243044,"uid":5150,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T15:28:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><br />\n仲有大陸好鍾意既<span style=\"color: red;\">發表講話</span>，<span style=\"color: orange;\">演講</span>唔會好d咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 係要跟返make announcement<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n</blockquote><br />\n呢個唔係歐式中文 係共式中文<br />\n講話已經係動詞 其一<br />\n演講都唔係最好<br />\n致辭 先係最純正嘅漢文term"},{"pid":"cad606dd987e0e1cfb441d335cd784e76ff9d1b2","tid":243044,"uid":21699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T16:13:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我地讀哲學成日用歐化中文，<br />\n語句越複雜，就越難避免。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實所有中文寫既學術論文，都無可避免要用歐化句<br />\n<br />\n因為（1）寫論文要precise， 而中文本身係講求美感，但唔準確既語言。同埋（2） 好多concepts都要借用英文詞彙，傳統中文冇呢個字，就唯有直釋英文做中文去表達，被逼使用歐化句。例如institutionalization，因為你想直接使用英文呢個詞彙意思，所以會直釋做「體制化」，雖然變左awkward的歐化句，但呢個係100%保留英文原意既用法。如果用傳統中文表達，唔多唔少都扭曲左個意思，影響傳達"},{"pid":"f02191706ffeecc5776721bf6b5b07eb8ee3589e","tid":243044,"uid":42764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T18:44:14.000Z","msg":"歐化句算唔算演變一種???"}]}